- @research_topics = ResearchTopic.all
.content-main-header
  %h1.f300 Rank the Research

.panel{ style: 'padding: 15px;'}
  %p.lead
    At MyApnea.Org you can help direct the future of sleep apnea research.
    Below are questions important to network members. Every month, you can
    cast up to five votes (and don't forget to suggest your own questions by
    clicking the
    = link_to 'Add a new research question', new_research_topic_path, class: 'btn btn-xs btn-primary'
    ). Top rated questions will be explored within the Forum. If data is
    lacking, the topic will be endorsed as an important direction for future
    research. Let your voice be heard, vote now!

- if current_user
  .panel.panel-rank-research
    %table.table
      - @research_topics.each do |research_topic|
        %tr
          %td
            %h1{ data: { toggle:'collapse', target:"#{'#progress'+research_topic.id.to_s}" } }
              %i.fa.fa-thumbs-o-up.fa-rank
          %td
            %h4= research_topic.text
            %p.f300.collapse{ id: "#{'ranking'+research_topic.id.to_s}" }
              = research_topic.description
            %p.f300.expand-topic{ data: { toggle:'collapse', target:"#{'#ranking'+research_topic.id.to_s}" } } Read more
            .collapse.progress{ style: 'width:90%;', id:"#{'progress'+research_topic.id.to_s}" }
              .progress-bar{ role:'progressbar', aria:{ valuenow:"#{research_topic.rating}", valuemin:'0', valuemax:'100' } }
                = research_topic.rating
